reviewText: Excellent workout video with great results
Cathe delivers once again. Great workout and the premixes are convenient,
You will be sweating like crazy when you get done with this work out. Very much worth the money. There is many premixes so you can do a short workout or a longer one.
You can never go wrong with Cathe Friedrich - this workout is no exception!  I definitely worked myself "To The Max" and can't wait until this comes back up in my workout rotation.
This is a great step DVD.  The routines are challenging but not complicated. Good workout.
